        <mxCell id="JnE91Lm5aDu9HKyyXbqy-3" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;1. User should be able to search a event based on some title, location and date&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;2. User should be able to view the details of the events (seats,description, metadata)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;3. User should be able to do a booking for that event&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
