        <mxCell id="t_DKb6i7VvN18Yv3edmi-2" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="Prevents double booking" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="60" x="690" y="2090" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="t_DKb6i7VvN18Yv3edmi-3" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="Provides high-speed filtering" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="70" x="760" y="1450" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="t_DKb6i7VvN18Yv3edmi-5" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(48, 48, 48); font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;&quot;&gt;When a user selects a seat, an entry is created in Redis with a 10-minute Time-to-Live (TTL), preventing other users from proceeding with the same seat.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-start-index=&quot;3890&quot; class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot; style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve; color: rgb(48, 48, 48); font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;If the payment is successful, the Redis entry is removed, the booking is confirmed in PostgreSQL, and the seat is permanently updated in Cassandra.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(48, 48, 48); font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;If the payment fails, the Redis entry automatically expires after 10 minutes, making the seat instantly available to others.&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="130" width="580" x="810" y="1980" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
